In  Table   III , the EHRXDiff and  EHRXDiff w  _  n  u  l  l subscript EHRXDiff w _ n u l l \text{EHRXDiff}_{w\_null} EHRXDiff start_POSTSUBSCRIPT italic_w _ italic_n italic_u italic_l italic_l end_POSTSUBSCRIPT  models achieve low FID scores, compared to SOTA text-conditional CXR generation models  [ 7 ]  with scores ranging from 3 to 9.
